summary:
Researcher and bilingual Lawyer, LLM in labour law and employment relations. Specialized on labour and employment law. Legal advisor with experience in law firms of high national and international reputation, resolution of labour legal inquiries in matters of individual and collective labour law, social security law. Legal advisor for national and multinational companies. With experience working in the legal area of ​​large public and private entities.

With training in labor law and social security, human rights and corporate social responsibility, as well as training in alternative dispute resolution mechanisms.
